<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Donate to Help Save Lives</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
        }
        /* Navigation Bar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #2c2c2c; /* Dark background */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #fff;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffcc00; /* Highlighted logo color */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .navbar .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .navbar .nav-links a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00; /* Highlight color on hover */
        }
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            background-image: url('https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5b5a266fcef372310148d6d6/1567460209464-IYTINWBNI8U2K1HNM2YY/20181225_165049%2B%25281%2529.jpg?format=2500w');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end; /* Align content to bottom */
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding-bottom: 100px; /* Add spacing below the text */
        }
        .text-container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* Semi-transparent background */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 700px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .hero-text {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .donation-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .donate-button {
            background-color: #2d8f5e;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .donate-button:hover {
            background-color: #24724b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="logo">TURTLE SHELTER PROJECT</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/about">ABOUT</a>
            <a href="/story">JEN'S STORY</a>
            <a href="/get-involved">GET INVOLVED</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="text-container">
            <div class="hero-text">DONATE TO HELP SAVE LIVES</div>
            <div class="donation-message">
                Each $30 tax-deductible donation to the Turtle Shelter Project will provide a high-tech foam vest for a youth or adult experiencing homelessness. You can tell us where you would like the vest or vests sent to, or we will send them to where there is the greatest need.
            </div>
            <form action="/realDonate" method="GET">
                <button type="submit" class="donate-button">Donate</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
